{\plain\f4\fs21\i\cf2\ulc2
Scope.
}
{\plain\f4\fs21\cf2\ulc2
 These rules apply to the provision of gifted and talented programs authorized in Iowa Code sections 257.42 to 257.49, for students who are identified as gifted and talented and who are enrolled in public school districts in this state.
}
\par
\pard\qj\sl250\tx340
{\plain\f4\fs21\cf2\ulc2
\tab
}
