{\plain\f4\fs21\cf2\ulc2
\tab
}
{\plain\f4\fs21\cf2\ulc2
Coordination time shall be made available to staff providing gifted and talented programs to allow staff to perform professional responsibilities.
}
\par
\pard\qj\sl250\tx340
{\plain\f4\fs21\cf2\ulc2
