{\plain\f4\fs21\i\cf2\ulc2
Financial management.
}
{\plain\f4\fs21\cf2\ulc2
 Gifted and talented funding is categorical funding and follows the general provisions in 281—Chapter 98.
}
\par
\pard\qj\sl250\tx340
